  "subject": "Modernise hv-ves docker images",
  "commit_message": "Modernise hv-ves docker images\n\n- use a eclipse-temuring jre alpine image to fix image\n  vulnerabilities and to use something non-custom\n- some small Dockerfile best practices (less layers,\n  entrypoint declaration at the end of the file)\n- bump snapshot version 1.11.1-SNAPSHOT\n- define changelog exclusions for submodules\n  that should not have changelog files since they\n  are not independently released\n\nIssue-ID: DCAEGEN2-3445\nChange-Id: Iddf1346cd2a44a17edd994a1121188eeb7ed7ef3\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
